The paper presents an improvement to the Ant Colony System algorithm for solving the Sequential Ordering Problem. This problem falls under the category of combinatorial optimization, which is often studied in the sub-fields of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
